{
  "id" : 757,
  "songNumber" : 145,
  "title" : "I HAVE LOST MY REPUTATION",
  "language" : "english",
  "originalKey" : "A",
  "capo" : 0,
  "bpm" : 0,
  "timeSignature" : "4/4",
  "hashtags" : [ ],
  "sections" : [ {
    "type" : "verse",
    "label" : "VERSE 1",
    "lines" : [ {
      "text" : "I have lost my reputation since I turned my back on sin",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 0
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 52
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "And a lot of friends went from me, since I let my Saviour in;",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 6
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 58
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Now they pass me by unknown, when they once passed with a smile;",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 9
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 58
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Now they say I'm very foolish, and they say I'm out of style.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 9
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 55
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : ""
    }, {
      "text" : "I am marked, marked, marked,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 5
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "I am marked now wherever I go;",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 20
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "I am marked, marked, marked,"
    }, {
      "text" : "Just what I am everyone seems to know.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 33
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : ""
    }, {
      "text" : "I am sealed, sealed, sealed,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 5
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "I am sealed by His Spirit Divine,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 19
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "O glory to God ! Hallelujah ! Amen !"
    }, {
      "text" : "I am His, and I know He is mine.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 27
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : ""
    }, {
      "text" : "Well, they say my life is ruined, and my talent thrown away,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 11
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 56
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "And they cannot understand it, for I had such plans one day;",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 9
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 56
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "But I know what I surrendered when I promised I'd go through;",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 6
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 53
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "And I gained far more glory since God made me over new.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 6
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 51
      } ]
    } ]
  } ]
}